  <brief_title>Intrathecal Atropine to Prevent Postoperative Nausea and Vomiting</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intravenous Dexamethasone Combined With Intrathecal Atropine to Prevent Morphine-related Nausea and Vomiting After Cesarean Delivery: A Randomized Double-blinded Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
